525
00:34:45.341 --> 00:34:48.821
for disabled people and their families. We thought that we were getting there.

526
00:34:49.540 --> 00:34:53.429
In 2017, the National Government primarily mandated the Enabling Good

527
00:34:53.500 --> 00:34:57.280
Lives approach. And when EGL came to our region, I was very,

528
00:34:57.340 --> 00:35:01.080
very cautious, knowing that I had already been part of many promises in the

529
00:35:01.140 --> 00:35:04.900
past to improve the way support is provided for disabled people.

