557
00:36:46.392 --> 00:36:49.032
The power moves away from disabled people and whanau.

558
00:36:49.462 --> 00:36:52.492
Power moves back towards systems, bureaucracy, and control.

559
00:36:53.192 --> 00:36:56.832
