580
00:38:10.652 --> 00:38:14.592
Others have experienced harm from support workers, services, and institutions

581
00:38:14.632 --> 00:38:18.192
that have been entrusted with their care. Their experiences matter.

582
00:38:18.692 --> 00:38:22.512
That is why the answer is not forcing disabled people to rely on

583
00:38:22.552 --> 00:38:25.672
family, and it is not forcing disabled people to rely on

584
00:38:25.772 --> 00:38:29.632
strangers. The answer is choice, real choice, choice

585
00:38:29.642 --> 00:38:31.332
that belongs to the disabled person.

586
00:38:31.952 --> 00:38:35.412
You have asked me what my solution is, and my solution is simple.

587
00:38:35.452 --> 00:38:39.092
Build a bill that trusts disabled people, protects supported

588
00:38:39.132 --> 00:38:42.752
decision-making, protects the right of disabled people to choose who

589
00:38:42.792 --> 00:38:46.352
