596
00:39:09.192 --> 00:39:11.232
This isn't resistance. This is grief.

597
00:39:12.032 --> 00:39:16.012
This is grief over the decades of advocacy that have been slipping away.

598
00:39:16.872 --> 00:39:20.332
Grief that trust is being replaced by control, grief that

599
00:39:20.372 --> 00:39:22.822
