2370
02:14:26.116 --> 02:14:28.656
We're already plugging system gaps every day.

2371
02:14:28.736 --> 02:14:31.056
My entire week is plugging system gaps.

2372
02:14:31.916 --> 02:14:34.896
There is no hidden reserve of capacity left to draw from.

2373
02:14:35.896 --> 02:14:39.236
And finally, the bill grants broad discretionary powers to any

2374
