2380
02:15:02.656 --> 02:15:06.446
families. We've heard about the significant spending on

2381
02:15:06.516 --> 02:15:10.186
disability, but shifting costs onto families does not

2382
02:15:10.216 --> 02:15:14.116
balance the books. It shifts those costs into the health and social welfare system,

2383
02:15:14.856 --> 02:15:18.736
as families will fall into crisis and poverty with poorer outcomes for

2384
