2390
02:15:42.206 --> 02:15:44.416
We do not need to become government employees.

2391
02:15:44.796 --> 02:15:48.376
What we need is legislation that recognizes the reality of complex

2392
02:15:48.416 --> 02:15:52.046
disability, preserves genuine partnership between families and

2393
02:15:52.076 --> 02:15:55.276
government, and protects the things that matter most to disabled people,

2394
02:15:55.996 --> 02:15:56.696
independence.

2395
02:15:57.676 --> 02:16:01.216
The stakes are simply too high to have legislation built on broad

2396
