Not implied, not assumed, written in.

2406
02:16:37.496 --> 02:16:41.116
My daughter is 13 years old. Her aspirations are reasonable.

2407
02:16:41.356 --> 02:16:44.796
She wants friends, independence, a job, and a life of her own.

2408
